    "title": "Utukufu wa Mungu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "utukufu wa mungu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p><em>Utukufu</em> katika Agano la Kale unamaanisha kitu tofauti na katika Kiingereza. Katika Kiingereza, mara nyingi inaelezea kitu cha muda mfupi, kama vile machweo au timu iliyoshinda mwaka uliopita.</p><p>Neno la Kiebrania kwa <em>utukufu</em> linamaanisha kile ambacho ni &quot;nzito&quot; au &quot;thabiti.&quot; Linarejelea &quot;umuhimu&quot; au &quot;thamani.&quot; Hii ni kinyume cha &quot;wakati mfupi&quot; au &quot;tupu.&quot; Utukufu wa Mungu unapojitokeza, siyo tu mwanga mkali au wingu linalong&apos;aa, bali ni ishara inayoonekana ya uhalisia wake kamili.</p><p>Utukufu wa Mungu unaonyesha uwepo, nguvu, na ukuu wake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28\">Ezekieli 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">10:4</a>). Utukufu wa Mungu unaweza kuonekana katika asili, kama wakati wa dhoruba au katika mapigo kwa Wamisri (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:2-Job37:5\">Ayubu 37:2–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3\">Zaburi 29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:7\">7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:21-Num14:22\">Hesabu 14:21–22</a>). Utukufu wa Mungu pia unaweza kuwa tukio maalum, kama Ufunuo kwenye Mlima Sinai (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:24\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 5:24</a>). Wakati Mungu alipoanzisha hema na hekalu la Mfalme Solomoni, utukufu wa Mungu ulijaza mahali hapo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">Kutoka 40:34–35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1 Wafalme 8:10–11</a>). Hii ilionyesha idhini na uwepo wake hapo. Vivyo hivyo, utukufu wa Bwana ulituma moto ulioanzisha dhabihu za kwanza katika patakatifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:22-Lev9:24\">Mambo ya Walawi 9:22–24</a>).</p><p>Wakati Mungu anaonyesha utukufu wake kupitia uumbaji wake, mara nyingi huitwa <em>theophany </em>(tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:16-Exod24:18\">Kutoka 24:16–18</a>). Mungu hutoa maoni ya kikomo ya utukufu wake kwa sababu anasema, &quot;hakuna mtu anayeweza kuniona na kuishi&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:18-Exod33:23\">Kutoka 33:18–23</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">Isaya 6:5</a>). Kumpa Mungu utukufu inamaanisha kuzungumza au kutenda kwa njia inayotambua Mungu ni nani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:19\">Yoshua 7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:15\">Isaya 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:16\">Yeremia 13:16</a>).</p><p>Yesu Kristo anaakisi utukufu na sura ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2 Wakorintho 4:4</a>). Kupitia kifo na ufufuo wake, Mungu alimtukuza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1-John17:5\">Yohana 17:1–5</a>). Yesu atakaporudi, ataonyesha utukufu wa Mungu katika ufalme wake uliorejeshwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:11\">Ufunuo 21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:23\">23</a>). Mtume Paulo anasema kwamba uwepo wa Kristo katika maisha ya Wakristo unathibitisha kwamba tutashiriki katika utukufu huo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">Warumi 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">Wakolosai 1:27</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:17-Exod14:18\">Kutoka 14:17–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:6-Exod16:12\">16:6–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:17-Exod33:23\">33:17–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:38\">40:34–38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:23-Lev9:24\">Mambo ya Walawi 9:23–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:3\">10:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:21-Num14:22\">Hesabu 14:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:24\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:19\">Yoshua 7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:11\">1 Wafalme 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1-2Chr7:3\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 7:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:2-Job37:5\">Ayubu 37:2–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:3\">Zaburi 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:4-Ps8:6\">8:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3\">29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:7-Ps29:9\">7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:8\">48:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3-Isa6:5\">Isaya 6:3–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:8\">42:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:7\">43:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:18-Isa66:19\">66:18–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:16\">Yeremia 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28\">Ezekieli 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:7\">Hosea 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1-John17:5\">Yohana 17:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">Warumi 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2 Wakorintho 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">Wakolosai 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:10-Rev21:11\">Ufunuo 21:10–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:23-Rev21:25\">23–25</a></p>",
